parameters:
Afterwards, I was violated by Suzuki for several hours. He
never wore a condom and ejaculated inside me. After the act

"...So? What were the results of the examination, doctor?"

had suggested that I get examined here because I had not
shown any signs of pregnancy for a long time. After a
lengthy period, today, the results of the examination were
finally revealed.

"Erm... It's difficult to say this but... Mr. Go's
girlfriend... seems to be... infertile."

"But... there's a treatment, right...? If we treat it, I can
eventually have a baby, right...?"

"It's likely that even with fertility treatments, the
condition won't improve... I'm truly sorry that we can't be
of more help..."
"No way...!! How can this... uuu... waaaah!!"

"Hey, hey, hey! This isn't a joke!! Are you saying she
really can't get pregnant!?"
"Young master, about that matter... may I have a word...?"

"It seems that the cause of the infertility is that
'Ramune'... Her numbers were off the charts. It was made by
one of your underlings, but this side effect is
problematic..."

"Tch...! Anyone using that stuff isn't right in the head to
begin with. They'd probably feel relieved not being able to
have kids!"

"...But seriously, she can't get pregnant? If 'Ramune' is
the cause, wouldn't things go back to normal if she stopped
taking it?"

"There's a possibility, but... I think it's quite low... At
least, it would take over a decade..."

"What?! It takes that long?! Ha... Just when I thought I
could have some fun making her pregnant, this totally kills
the mood..."

"Uuuu... I'm sorry, Darling... I... can't get pregnant with
your baby..."

"Don't worry about it, Makoto! I'll take good care of you!
Cheer up!"

I continued to cry in Go's arms for what seemed like
forever. Not being able to get pregnant was truly shocking,
but Go's words genuinely made me happy. For the first time,
I felt love for Go and wanted to do anything he wished for.
